{% extends "base.jinja2" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container_12">
  <div class="wrapper indent-bottom4">
    <div class="grid_12 last-col">
      <div class="bg-color5">
        <h3 class="box-title">Infant/Toddler Program</h3>
        <div class="indents">
          <p class="wrapper">
            Here at Sunny Meadows Child Care, we are reponsive to all aspects of
            children's development. By using defined practices of the Infant-Toddler
            development; caregivers develop close, supportive relationships with
            the children in their care and their families.
          </p>
          <p class="wrapper">
            Our caregivers support children's natural desire to be active learners.
            We create an active learning enviroment for infacts and toddlers that
            meet all their needs - their social and emotional, physical and cognitive
            needs. Their programs purpose is to ensure that your child's first year
            of learning is a positive experience in a warm and caring enviroment, 
            where children can learn in a group settings, and also individually.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-color0">
        <h3 class="box-title">Preschool Program</h3>
        <div class="indents">
          <p class="wrapper">
            In our preschool class, children start learning numbers, counting,
            the alphabet, beginning pencil skills, color and shape names,
            small and large motor development, hand-eye coordination spatial 
            awareness, music melody and rhythm. We offer activities to
            introduce and foster the growth and development. We provide a 
            caring, loving, learning enviroment that is developmentally appropriate
            for each child's interest and needs. We help prepare them for 
            kindergarten by building onto skills they already learned.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-color1">
        <h3 class="box-title">Before & After School Program</h3>
        <div class="indents">
          <p class="wrapper">
            We provide indoor and outdoor activities, we offer arts and crafts,
            reading time, and we also have game time (game time is limited per
            day). School-age children can also work on homework after school before
            parents pick them up.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
